{"date":"2006-02-15","platform":"其他","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/b1/5e/73341_q0572.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/b1/5e/73341_q0572.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/b1/5e/73341_q0572.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/b1/5e/73341_q0572.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/b1/5e/73341_q0572.jpg"},"summary":"很多年前，年青的丹麦诗人凯尔·格鲁森突感灵感丧失，这令他万分苦恼。某天，他在图书馆读到挪威女作家西格丽德·温塞特的小说《新娘，主人，十字架》，凯尔为西格丽德的文才所折服，决定启程前往挪威拜访这位女作家以寻找灵感。他落脚在西格丽德一个远房亲戚的农场，并在此结识了美丽的女孩伊吉博格，两个年轻人陷入热恋。然而伊吉博格的父亲已将女儿许配给一个粗俗丑陋的男孩，凯尔被迫和爱人分开，带着无限落寞返回丹麦。时光流转，岁月飞逝，身处挪威的伊吉博格和远在丹麦的凯尔久久思念着对方，时刻等待着再次相逢……\r\n\r\n本片荣获2007年第79届奥斯卡最佳动画短片奖。","name":"The Danish Poet","name_cn":"丹麦诗人","tags":[{"name":"短片","count":38,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":18,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奥斯卡","count":17,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2006","count":15,"total_cont":0},{"name":"恋爱","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"偶尔与必然","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"邂逅","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧洲","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000s","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"平静","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"挪威","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"诗人","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"温馨","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"爱情","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TorillKove","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"AM","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画短片","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"其它","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"US","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"加拿大","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"丹麦诗人"},{"key":"上映年度","value":"2006年2月15日"},{"key":"片长","value":"14min"},{"key":"官方网站","value":"www.onf.ca/webextension/thedanishpoet"},{"key":"导演","value":"Torill Kove"},{"key":"编剧","value":"Torill Kove"},{"key":"主演","value":"丽芙·乌曼"},{"key":"类型","value":"爱情 / 动画 / 短片"},{"key":"制片国家/地区","value":"加拿大 / 挪威"},{"key":"语言","value":"英语"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"}],"rating":{"rank":2631,"total":54,